Kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'abandura Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Afurika y'u Burayi (EEA) no mu Bwongereza.
Igaragaza ko ubwandu bw'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) bukomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ibihugu by'ibanze by'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose, ariko mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu.
Ukurikije ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima byita ku barwayi ba mu mutwe bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabo ku buryo bw'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, mu ntara ya Hubei, hatangajwe ko hari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibihaha kitaramenyekana.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cyo mu Bushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko cyamenye ko hari ikintu cyateje indwara ya coronavirus, ubu cyitwa SARS-CoV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bagaragaza indwara y'ibihaha cyangwa indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe, kandi abenshi barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 yagize uburwayi bukomeye cyane bukeneye kuvurwa mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6% barwaye cyane bakenera ubuvuzi bw'indembe.
Umubare w'abandura COVID-19 bajya mu bitaro ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugiye gusuzuma uko COVID-19 ishobora kwiyongera mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) tugereranyije n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri Leta zigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Afurika Yunze Ubumwe y'Ubukungu (EEA) n'u Bwongereza mu gihe cy'umwaka, kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, n'umubare w'abanduye muri iki gihe mu Butaliyani.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira kugaragara mu Bushinwa, cyakomeje gukwirakwira mu tundi duce, bituma ibindi bihugu byo ku isi bikomeza kwibasirwa na COVID-19.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ikinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe, cyatangaje ko icyorezo cya mbere cya COVID-19 mu banyarwanda cyemejwe hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'icyorezo cya OMS.
Abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe muri EU/EEA bagaragaye mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020, bagarukaga mu gihugu cyabo bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu 30 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) byatangaje ko byavumbuye ubwandu bwa COVID-19, aho byageze ku bantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu gihe mu gihugu kimwe cy'u Butaliyani hari abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Kubona imibare y'ibyago byo kwandura no kwandura COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) gisoza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo, itangwa n'abakozi b'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'iz'akarere, n'ibindi bisobanuro byemewe n'amategeko, nk'ibya OMS.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagereranywa uko bimeze mu bihugu byabo n'uko bimeze mu Butaliyani.
Dufatiye ku bipimo by'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 muri iki gihe, tuzabaze imibare y'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu bihugu 7 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 yose uhereye ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, kandi tuzabaze ko ari igipimo gisanzwe cya COVID-19.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imimerere y'ibanze ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Afurika y'Ubukungu y'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza, muri rusange ni nk'uw'abanduye mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma igenda yiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (mu nyandiko y'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mu Butaliyani, aho ibihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza na byo byagize ukwiyongera nk'uko mu bipimo byo gukurikirana (data).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza ingano y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani.
Mu byumweru bitatu no munsi yaho, ibihugu 15 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza byatangaje imibare y'abarwayi bose ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ingana n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza wiyongereye cyane.
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 byagaragajwe n'abashakashatsi, igaragaza ko icyorezo kiri kwiyongera ku kigero kimwe mu bihugu byose.
Ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange ku rwego rw'igihugu ku byiciro bitandukanye, ku mpamvu zitandukanye, kandi bikomeje gukora nubwo hari itandukaniro hagati y'ibihugu mu buryo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, harimo n'ibisobanuro by'icyorezo n'ibipimo.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce twanduye mu Butaliyani batangaje ko abagera ku 10% by'abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurwa mu buryo bwagutse, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe byo muri utwo duce byamaze kugera ku gipimo cyabyo cyo kuvurwa.
Ku rwego rw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA), amakuru y'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi cyane ari 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntasobanuwe) kuri buri ruhande.
Ariko kandi, ibyo bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bikomeze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi y'ibanze yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU n'ibyo mu gihe cy'ubukonje mu Burayi utandukanye cyane mu bihugu bitandukanye, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29,2 ku bantu 100,000, mu gihe muri Porutugali hari ibitanda 4,2.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo gukoresha ibikoresho byinshi ariko bikanabikoresha bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (mu 2010-11 bwari bufite ibitanda 12,5 by'indwara z'ububabare bukabije n'ubw'ububabare buciriritse ku bantu 100,000).
Ibipimo by'ibyiyumvo byakozwe bijyanye no kurengera umubare w'abantu bashobora guhabwa ubuvuzi byashyizwe mu igenzura rya gatandatu rya ECDC Rapid COVID-19 Risk Assessment, hamwe n'ibyerekezo by'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro, bifitanye isano n'ibyago byo kurenga 90% by'umubare w'ibitanda byakira mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Kubera ko iyi ndwara yibasiye ibihugu bya EU/EEA ndetse n'utundi duce tumwe na tumwe tw'Ubwongereza, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikunze kwita ku baturage bahatuye, amakuru ajyanye n'ibyorezo n'umubare w'ibitanda byo mu bitaro by'indembe bigomba kuboneka hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kubara amakuru ku byiciro by'ibiro by'indembe by'akarere (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima byita ku barwayi bari mu byihutirwa, bigomba rero guhangana n'ikibazo cyo kwandura kwa virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu karere, no kwitegura kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe, nk'uko byagenze mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago bya vuba aha rya ECDC, guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2 birasaba uburyo bwihuse, bwiteguye kandi bunini bwo kwirinda indwara, hamwe no guhinduka kuva ku buryo bwo kugabanya ku buryo bwo kugabanya. Iyo umubare w'abarwayi wiyongereye cyane nkuko byitezwe, kutagira imyiteguro bishobora gutuma abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro batabona umwanya uhagije wo gusobanukirwa no guhangana n'ikibazo.
Mu byiciro by'ibanze by'ibyago, ibipimo by'ibyago by'ibiza byerekana ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zishobora gufatwa mu kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari amahirwe y'igihe gito ku bihugu byo kongera imbaraga mu bikorwa byo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
