Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura ubushakashatsi buri gukorwa ku gice gishya cy'ibikubiyemo cyahindutse vuba.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na CoV, nk'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (indwara ya MERS yatangiriye mu 2012).
