CoVs ni indwara zidakunze guteza abantu indwara, ahanini zitera 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe byo mu cyiciro cya 4.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twabonye CoV ebyiri zanduza abantu cyane: SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012 kandi bidatinze zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu zifite ubwandu n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ibi bituma icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kiba icya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
