CoV ni ubwoko bw'agakoko gatera SIDA gashya, kaba gatuwe n'inkingo nini z'umukondo umwe wa RNA, kandi gafite ADN.
Zishobora gutandukanywa mu byiciro bine: alpha, beta, gamma na delta, aho alpha- na beta-CoV zishobora kwanduza abantu.
Muri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, poroteyine yitwa Envelope Spike ((S)) ikora mu buryo bw'uruhu rw'uruhu nyuma yo kwambikwa ku byuma byayo by'ibanze byitwa ACE2 na DPP4.
