Virusi ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byombi byaturutse ku ndwara z'ingurube, kandi birazwi ko byandujwe ku bantu binyuze mu ngurube z'ingurube n'ingamiya.
Kugereranya kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi virusi zanduza virusi, byagaragaje ko virusi nshya ihuriyeho na 96% na SARS-CoVs mu ducurama twitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21, bituma dutekereza ko ducurama ari byo byakomotseho SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, uwo muvuduko wa interineti watumye virusi ivamo ubwoko bw'ubwoko butandukanye ikagera ku bantu nturamenyekana, kandi inzira y'ubwandu iracyari mu rujijo.
Ji n'abandi bagaragaje ko inzoka zishobora kuba ari zo zitwara virusi mu gihe zinyura mu bantu, kubera ko izo mpinduka zose ziri muri poroteyine ya S zifite ubwoko bumwe.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwagaragaje ko coronavirus (CoV) na SARS-CoV-2 mu bipande by'ingurube zifite ihurizo rya genome ya virusi ku kigero cya 99%, kandi ko ibipande by'ingurube z'ibinyamanswa birya ibimonyo bifite iminwa miremire bikunze gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, bishobora kuba ari byo bikurikirana virusi ya SARS-CoV-2, nk'uko bivugwa n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa.
