Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'abarwaye cyane, bagomba gupimwa hakiri kare kugira ngo bamenye niba baranduye virusi, ndetse no mu gihe nta bimenyetso bya paruve bigaragara.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu karere ka Gicurasi 2019, bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwaye barwaye, 76% barwaye inkorora, 55% barwaye guhumeka nabi na 3% barwaye isesemi, naho 8% by'abarwayi bakeneraga imashini ibafasha guhumeka.
