Ariko 80% muri bo bakeneye ibikoresho byo guhumeka, ibyo bikaba biruta cyane umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19, ndetse bisa n'aho ari kimwe n'ibyorezo bya MERS biteza urupfu kurusha COVID-19.
Mu barwayi ba MERS, harimo n'uburwayi bw'igifu (mu kigero cya 26%) n'ububabare bw'izuru (mu kigero cya 21%).
Mu barwayi ba SARS, uburwayi (99% kugeza 100%), inkorora yoroheje (29% kugeza 75%), guhumeka nabi (40% kugeza 42%), igifu kidakira (20 kugeza 25%) n'ububabare bw'izuru (13 kugeza 25%) ni ibimenyetso by'ingenzi, kandi hafi 14% kugeza 20% by'abarwayi bakeneye ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
