Ibisubizo by'iki kizamini bishobora gutuma hamenyekana umubare nyawo w'abahitanwa n'iki cyorezo n'urwego rw'ubwirinzi bw'ingurube mu baturage.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyashoboraga gutanga amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo kubera ingamba zo gupima.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini ku bantu barenga 3% mu baturage bacyo, kandi umubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu bihugu byinshi uratandukanye cyane.
Ibi kandi bisa n'ibyagize ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, aho imibare y'abapfa mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe yariyongereye cyane.
Ikoreshwa mu gihe nyacyo rya polymerase chain reverse transcription (rRT-PCR) rishobora kugeragezwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byakozwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo by'umwotsi wo mu mazuru cyangwa ibipimo by'amahembe.
Mu by'ukuri, ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igikorwa cya RT-PCR cyakozwe hakoreshejwe ibibyimba byo mu muhogo gishobora kwiringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma, virusi irahita ikwira mu bihaha, igashira mu muhogo.
Mu cyumweru cya kabiri, abanduye bashobora gupimwa bakoresheje ibipimo by'ibice by'umubiri binyuze mu muyoboro w'umwuka w'imbere mu nda cyangwa mu gusohora amazuru (umuhogo).
Muri Mutarama 2020, ikigo Charité cy'i Berlin cyakoze igerageza rya mbere rya PCR rikoresheje uburyo bwa Real-Time Polymerase Chain Reverse Transcription (rRT-PCR), ritanga ibyangombwa by'ibikoresho 250,000 byo gupima byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
