Iyi virusi ishobora kubaho ku bipimo by'abantu mu gihe cy'amasaha 72.
Nubwo hashobora kubaho ubwandu mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso no mu byiciro bya nyuma by'indwara, igihe cy'amezi atatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni cyo cy'ingenzi cyane. Uburyo bwemewe bwo gupima ni gukoresha uburyo bwo gupima mu gihe nyacyo bwa transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu gusomana kw'amazuru n'umunwa.
